Definition: deliberately deviating from what is good
Example: there will always be a few people who, through macho perversity, gain satisfaction from bullying and terrorism
Synonyms: adj, all, corrupt, perverse, perverseness, evil, deliberately, deviating, from, what, is, good, there, will, always, be, a, few, people, who, through, macho, gain, satisfaction, bullying, and, terrorism
Category: noun.attribute
